---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Lucy Russell Hair â€“ Calm, sensory-friendly hair services"
  description="Calm, sensory-friendly hair services at home in Bournemouth, Poole and surrounding areas. Mobile hairdressing for neurodivergent clients and carers."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-10 m-4">
    <div class="grid gap-8 prose lg:prose-xl xl:prose-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">
        Sensory-friendly mobile hairdressing in Bournemouth &amp; Poole
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Calm, sensory-friendly mobile hairdressing at home in Bournemouth, Poole
        and surrounding areas (within 25 miles), specialising in neurodivergent
        clients, carers and anyone who prefers quiet, predictable appointments.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/book" class="btn btn-info px-6 py-3 text-base">
          Book a quiet appointment
        </a>
        <a
          href="/before-your-visit"
          class="btn btn-outline btn-secondary px-6 py-3 text-base"
        >
          Before your visit
        </a>
      </div>

      <section class="mt-6" aria-labelledby="reassurance-heading">
        <h2 id="reassurance-heading" class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">
          What to expect
        </h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-base-content/90">
          <li>Sensory-aware training: your comfort comes first</li>
          <li>Home visits only: no busy salons</li>
          <li>No surprises: we agree what happens before we start</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-6" aria-labelledby="services-heading">
        <h2 id="services-heading" class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">
          Services Lucy offers
        </h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-base">
          <li>Mobile haircuts at home (short and long hair)</li>
          <li>Fringe trims and tidy-ups between cuts</li>
          <li>Gentle restyles at your pace</li>
          <li>Sensory-friendly appointments for neurodivergent clients</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4" aria-labelledby="bio-heading">
        <h2 id="bio-heading" class="text-xl font-semibold">Lucy Russell</h2>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
          Lucy has years of experience in hairdressing and focuses on home
          visits and calm environments. She works in Bournemouth, Poole and
          surrounding areas (within 25 miles).
        </p>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
          Lucy has training in sensory awareness and neurodiversity-friendly
          practice. She is committed to following your preferences and pace: you
          say what you need (e.g. quiet, breaks, dry cut, step-by-step
          explanations), and she will work with you.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section
        class="border-t border-base-300 pt-6"
        aria-labelledby="approach-heading"
      >
        <h2 id="approach-heading" class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">
          How Lucy works
        </h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-base">
          <li>Home visits only: no busy salons</li>
          <li>Consultation first: we agree what happens before we start</li>
          <li>Your pace: breaks and changes are always okay</li>
          <li>
            Clear communication: by email, text or phone, whatever you prefer
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div
        class="aspect-square max-w-xs rounded-lg bg-base-200 flex items-center justify-center text-base-content/50"
      >
        <span class="text-sm">Photo of Lucy (optional)</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
